trans-unit.source: Compiles <xref href="System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument"></xref> and XML-format grammar files into binary grammar files with the .cfg extension and sends the output to a stream.
trans-unit.target: Kompilerer <xref href="System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument"> </xref> og XML-format grammatikk filer i binære grammatikk filer med filtypen alle cfg sender utdata til en dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: You compile <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> objects and XML-format grammars to a binary format to optimize them for loading and consumption by a speech recognition engine.
trans-unit.target: Du kompilerer <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>objekter og XML-format grammars til et binært format til å optimalisere dem for innlasting og forbruk av en motor for talegjenkjenning.</xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>

trans-unit.source: Compiling a speech recognition grammar using one of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarCompiler.Compile%2A> methods can reduce the amount of time required to construct a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> or an XML-format grammar.
trans-unit.target: Beregner en tale recognition grammatikk for den <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarCompiler.Compile%2A>metoder kan redusere tiden som kreves for å lage en <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>objekt fra en <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>eller en XML-format grammatikk.</xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> </xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> </xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarCompiler.Compile%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Compile SRGS Grammars](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/dbdd9e2b-62c7-4938-be84-3dcc77ad454a).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [kompileres SRGS Grammars](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/dbdd9e2b-62c7-4938-be84-3dcc77ad454a).

trans-unit.source: Compiles an XML-format grammar file into a binary grammar file with the .cfg extension and sends the output to a stream.
trans-unit.target: Kompilerer en XML-grammatikk-fil til en binær grammatikk-fil med filtypen alle cfg og sender utdata til en dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: The XML-format grammar file must conform to the [Speech Recognition Grammar Specification (SRGS) Version 1.0](http://www.w3.org/TR/speech-grammar/).
trans-unit.target: XML-format grammatikk filen må samsvare med den [tale Recognition grammatikk spesifikasjonen (SRGS) versjon 1.0](http://www.w3.org/TR/speech-grammar/).

trans-unit.source: When accessing files, a security check is performed when the file is created or opened.
trans-unit.target: Når du åpner filer, utføres en sikkerhetskontroll når filen opprettes eller åpnes.

trans-unit.source: The security check is typically not done again unless the file is closed and reopened.
trans-unit.target: Sikkerhetskontrollen vanligvis gjøres ikke på nytt hvis filen lukkes og åpnes på nytt.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Compile SRGS Grammars](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/dbdd9e2b-62c7-4938-be84-3dcc77ad454a).
